%% Diagram: Two-Phase Commit happy path and the blocking failure mode
%% Type: sequence
%%{init: {'htmlLabels': false}}%%
sequenceDiagram
    participant C as Coordinator
    participant P1 as Participant 1
    participant P2 as Participant 2

    note over C,P2: Phase 1 — Prepare (vote)
    C->>P1: PREPARE
    C->>P2: PREPARE
    P1->>P1: log, lock
    P2->>P2: log, lock
    P1-->>C: VOTE-YES
    P2-->>C: VOTE-YES

    note over C,P2: Phase 2 — Commit (decide)
    C->>C: log COMMIT
    C->>P1: COMMIT
    C->>P2: COMMIT
    P1-->>C: ACK
    P2-->>C: ACK

    note over C,P2: Failure: coordinator crash after PREPARE
    C-xC: crash
    note over P1,P2: YES-voters hold locks.\nNo decision: cannot commit.\nMight have committed: cannot abort.\nBlock until recovery.
